{"tid":1496803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要為全港市民帶黎思想上既轉變","createTime":"2019-08-22T16:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:33:43.000Z","uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe4da1e70f5aec01f642daa6d9dfad5af3392f8","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係再叫香港人 加油<br />\n<br />\n香港人咩都可以加油，藍絲可以加油，警察可以加油，連電視台都可以加油。<br />\n<br />\n但唯香港人唔可以再淨係加油<br />\n<br />\n當政不以民為本既時候，仲唔反抗等幾時？<br />\n<br />\n大叫香港人 反抗！<br />\n<br />\n要由言語入手慢慢解開全港市民既思想同政制束縛！<br />\n<br />\n反抗只係思想轉變上即中轉站<br />\n<br />\n最終既目標係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n<br />\n_________</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a1cd2d1b10f5316df5182f5a5475e9895a7a137","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:28:41.000Z","msg":"連結全港市民反抗既口號就係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd3cacebee8207147f1286e53c13614143d7acb","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4aa4102d6154411b569bf51c05f48a4b62c4596","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔係全港市民都會上連登<br />\n<br />\n要轉思想由連登帶落民間"},{"pid":"b1437e5fa7327a812f71531c9833463ca2683b55","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4aa4102d6154411b569bf51c05f48a4b62c4596","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔係全港市民都會上連登<br />\n<br />\n要轉思想由連登帶落民間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"將思想"},{"pid":"3464bd78a00796beabd8defdeba3705b8ffa6d83","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1437e5fa7327a812f71531c9833463ca2683b55","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4aa4102d6154411b569bf51c05f48a4b62c4596","tid":1496803,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔係全港市民都會上連登<br />\n<br />\n要轉思想由連登帶落民間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"將思想"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"一黎就時代革命未必全港接受<br />\n<br />\n但想將反抗意識融入民間好重要<br />\n<br />\n就好似溫水煮蛙咁<br />\n<br />\n呢個只不過係反向版，慢慢令大家思想開放"}]}